title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - PMDG Boeing 737-700
description:
Yesterday the long waiting was awarded by PMDG the Boeing 737-700 was released during the EMEA hours. It resulted in some store issues because so many wanted to buy this aircraft that the site went on black for a specific period. The Boeing 737-700 is the first on the series of 737's which will be released by PMDG and as always it is high quality just like the earlier released DC6. The 737-700 is available in 3 versions: the passenger version (737-700), the cargo version (737-700BDSF) and the business jet version (737-700BBJ). All 3 versions are delivered with multiple liveries.

00:00 intro
00:10 PMDG operations center
03:17 review of aircraft types and liveries
05:28 business jet version (747-700BBJ) and cockpit
20:43 cargo version (747-700BDSF)
25:55 passenger version (747-700)

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
